    student_name VARCHAR(50),
    enrollment_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE CourseRegistrations (
    course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    course_name VARCHAR(50),
    department VARCHAR(50),
    instructor_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Grades (
    grade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    course_id INT,
    grade VARCHAR(2)
)

### STATEMENT

UPSERT INTO CourseRegistrations (course_id, course_name, department, instructor_name) VALUES (107, 'Physics 101', 'Physics', 'Professor Taylor') ON CONFLICT (course_id) DO UPDATE SET course_name = 'Physics 101', department = 'Physics', instructor_name = 'Professor Taylor';
